productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Georgie has one of these. She works as a busboy and she says it looks brown.
My neighbor Lular has one of these. She works as a cake decorator and she says it looks ragged.
My neighbor Elisha has one of these. She works as a fortune teller and she says it looks floppy.
This sensor works considerably well. It mildly improves my basketball by a lot.
